info.name: Rajma Chawal Rice Bowl (Serves 1)
info.description: Our Rajma Chawal Rice Bowl features a generous portion of fragrant, fluffy basmati rice, cooked to perfection. Paired with it is our flavorful and hearty Rajma curry, which is simmered in a tomato-based gravy infused with a blend of aromatic spices. The result is a delightful, mildly spiced curry that's both savory and satisfying.

info.name: Aloo Gobhi & Boondi Raita Meal (Serves 1)
info.description: Savor a classic Indian trio: Aloo Gobhi, paired with refreshing Boondi Raita, and 3 soft, warm Chapatis. The hearty, spiced cauliflower and potatoes blend perfectly with the cool raita. Together with the freshly made chapatis, it's a satisfying, balanced meal that captures the essence of Indian comfort food. Ideal for lunch or dinner, this combination promises a harmonious medley of flavors.
